title: [Solindago Anox]
description: Thickly needled pine trees border the path, overhanging the walkway that branches off to the northwest to the extent that it looks like a tunnel through the greenery.  The white gravel that lines the path is covered with a fine layer of pink sandstone dust from the rocky rise to the north.
